fun arrangeCoins(coins: IntArray): Int {
    val n = coins.size
    var left = 0
    var right = n - 1

        val mid = (left + right) / 2

import java.lang.Math

fun complexNumbersExponential(complex: ComplexNumber): ComplexNumber {
    val real = complex.real.toDouble()
    val imag = complex.imag.toDouble()
    val cos = Math.cos(real)
    val sin = Math.sin(imag)
    val result = ComplexNumber(cos, sin)
    return result
}

fun main() {
    val complex = ComplexNumber(2.718281828459045, 0.0)
    val result = complexNumbersExponential(complex)
    println(result)
}
